{"tid":1350014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個廢青，今日喺立場出咗一篇文","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:26:22.000Z","uid":120631,"like":181,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"4e0f136f7955f8b0acc6b1eda49b1bbeefd507d0","tid":1350014,"uid":120631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:44:32.000Z","msg":"我係一個啱啱u grad嘅廢青，未搵工返緊垃圾pt<br />\n由六月到而家歷時43日嘅民主運動<br />\n幾乎所有行動我都會參與<br />\n企過前線都做過和理非傳下物資叫下口號<br />\n不合作運動連塞地鐵我都試過<br />\n<br />\n但係 香港入面仲有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚多港猪<br />\n無錯，真係好撚多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n單單係我間u都有好多呢啲不問世事嘅自私撚<br />\n琴晚嘅事好多人終於肯發聲表態<br />\n但佢哋只係抱怨緊點解香港會搞成咁<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我今日終於忍唔住寫咗篇文俾立場<br />\n一間良心傳媒<br />\n多謝佢哋幫我出咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%87%B4%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%94%E7%BE%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25B2%2589%25E9%25BB%2598%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25BE%2594%25E7%25BE%258A%2F&d=h%2FjpO%2F4vOxs1xnBU3UKRHhmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=d63243d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%25B2%2589%25E9%25BB%2598%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25BE%2594%25E7%25BE%258A%2F&h=fd4551e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%87%B4%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%94%E7%BE%8A/</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗親身出去發夢之外<br />\n我都唔知可以再做啲咩先幫到香港<br />\n所以我只係想用自己擅長嘅文字，嘗試一下喚醒群眾<br />\n<br />\n有無用，唔知<br />\n但起碼我做過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n香港人，唔撚準放棄<br />\n大家要各施其職<br />\n記得，勿忘初衷<br />\n一齊行落去！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"8d69ea5c53fbc9650392b5ceb0ec1c79c0f111d8","tid":1350014,"uid":84396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"740cd216e7a7b5b92993f6fc0c0279709debe1f0","tid":1350014,"uid":177813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9634e0202b202a1eca3171c586fd4e3e8841db00","tid":1350014,"uid":138402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"1b6dfc5e4e5cd6999b96ba7e08379cc96e1805d2","tid":1350014,"uid":135623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d18304be2e5ea6abac8a3742c1c3fd53c3c852","tid":1350014,"uid":231859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"1a494e47d5a98e499b49d9332cd1e6d1b76f31f4","tid":1350014,"uid":1731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"當發生左咁多事d港豬都唔肯醒嘅話<br />\n佢地已經冇得救"},{"pid":"352f792c6b6b4ee468201b62af3f74a846751882","tid":1350014,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"做咩唔用筆名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c211b88617dcf24e394330e3172a2d1e7b74012","tid":1350014,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T